rows.label: tlk401008_msg0001
rows.name:
Nothing untoward is going on
in the Superbian army, I assure you.

rows.label: tlk401008_msg0002
rows.name:
Those who have come to Acedia belong
to the Carraig Imperial Guard.

rows.label: tlk401008_msg0003
rows.name:
Elite soldiers who have sworn solemn
oaths to protect the Emperor.

rows.label: tlk401008_msg0004
rows.name:
So if anything suspicious were
going on, I'd venture it would have
to be on the Invidian side...

rows.label: tlk401008_msg0005
rows.name:
I find it difficult to tell what those
people are thinking sometimes.
